This memo documents the task performed.

We processed all 15 IDs listed in `list.txt` and created two subjective, emotionally resonant title files (one in English and one in Japanese) for each ID based on their respective `tags` and `critique` contents.

All 30 title files (e.g., `<ID>.en.txt` and `<ID>.ja.txt`) have been successfully generated and saved into the `title/` directory as requested.